quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,1,"Kāf hā yā ‘aēn sọ̄d. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  19,2,"(Èyí ni) ìrántí nípa ìkẹ́ tí Olúwa Rẹ ṣe fún ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀ (Ànábì) Zakariyyā.",""
  19,3,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ ní ìpè ìkọ̀kọ̀.",""
  19,4,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, dájúdájú eegun ara mi ti lẹ, orí (mi) ti kún fún ewú, èmi kò sì níí pasán nípa bí mo ṣe ń pè Ọ́, Olúwa mi.",""
  19,5,"Àti pé dájúdájú mò ń páyà àwọn ìbátan mi lẹ́yìn (ikú) mi. Ìyàwó mi sì jẹ́ àgàn. Nítorí náà, ta mí lọ́rẹ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ ọmọ rere kan,",""
  19,6,"(tí) ó máa jogún mi, tí ó sì máa jogún àwọn ẹbí (Ànábì) Ya‘ƙūb. Kí O sì ṣe é ní ẹni tí O yọ́nú sí, Olúwa mi.”",""
  19,7,"Zakariyyā, dájúdájú Àwa máa fún ọ ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ọmọkùnrin kan, orúkọ rẹ̀ ni Yahyā. A kò fún ẹnì kan ní (irú) orúkọ (yìí) rí ṣíwájú (rẹ̀).",""
  19,8,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, báwo ni mo ṣe máa ní ọmọ nígbà tí ìyàwó mi jẹ́ àgàn, tí mo sì ti di àgbàlagbà gan-an.”",""
  19,9,"(Mọlāika) sọ pé: “Báyẹn ni (ó máa rí).” Olúwa rẹ sọ pé: “Ó rọrùn fún Mi. Mó kúkú dá ìwọ náà ṣíwájú (rẹ̀), nígbà tí ìwọ kò tí ì jẹ́ n̄ǹkan kan.”",""
  19,10,"(Zakariyyā) sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, fún mi ní àmì kan.” (Mọlāika) sọ pé: “Àmì rẹ ni pé, o ò níí lè bá ènìyàn sọ̀rọ̀ fún ọjọ́ mẹ́ta, kì í ṣe ti àmódi.”",""
  19,11,"Nígbà náà, ó jáde sí àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ láti inú ilé ìjọ́sìn. Ó sì tọ́ka sí wọn pé kí wọ́n máa ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ (fún Allāhu) ní òwúrọ̀ àti ní ìrọ̀lẹ́.",""
